title: mStable Association funding proposal
body:
A [post](https://forum.mstable.org/t/mstable-association-genesis-grant-request/380) has been shared on the mStable forum by James Simpson on behalf of the mStable Swiss Association. It has received widespread support from the broader community, and it is proposed that the mStableDAO present this proposal from the Swiss Association to Meta Governors for a formal vote.

**Are you in favour of this being done?**
author: 0x4B37BbC8CAb32aade27Ce8b1bb2A9E614de81E03
